{{Quote|And ''then'' we get drunk? Last cantina we were at, there was this little Twi'lek who I just ''know'' was hot for me... <small>Only I was out of creds and she only drinks Tatooine Sunrises...</small>|Jariah Syn|<ref name="SWG">[[Legacy (2006) 37|''Legacy'' (2006) 37]]</ref>}}
A '''Tatooine Sunburn''', also known as a '''Tatooine Sunrise''', was an [[Alcohol/Legends|intoxicating]] beverage consisting of two [[Starshine Surprise]]s in the same glass.<ref name="GG9" /> It was a rough drink that was said to put the drinker under the table quick to the benefit of nearby thieves.<ref name="swg">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=item|Tatooine Sunburn}}</ref>

[[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] Sunburn was served at the [[Bantha Traxx]] on the planet [[Lianna/Legends|Lianna]] where it cost 7 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] per glass<ref name="WHSV">''[[Wretched Hives of Scum & Villainy]]''</ref>.

The [[Gusha's Luck]] [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] also sold Tatooine Sunburn for an increased price. [[Jariah Syn]] expressed disappointment when he learned a [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] patron only drank that particular drink, as he was low on credits. However, he approached her anyway and the two had good time until the woman's furious husband chased Jariah away.

